    "starRating": "FIVE",
    "comment": "Nafta no cargo allí....pero....el restaurante es excelente.....minutas, carnes, pastas, bebidas grandes, todo muy bueno, muy recomendable para el que está de paso o laburando....\n\nLos mozos muy atentos, los precios razonables,  el café en vaso premium.\n\nPárrafo para Rubén, el mozo Santiagueño de Termas, es un capo, la deja chiquitita.....\n\n(Translated by Google)\nI don\u0027t fill up there... but... the restaurant is excellent... quick meals, meats, pasta, large drinks, everything is very good, highly recommended for anyone passing through or working...\n\nThe waiters are very attentive, the prices are reasonable, and the coffee is served in premium cups.\n\nA special mention for Rubén, the waiter from Termas de Río Hondo in Santiago del Estero; he\u0027s a pro, he blows everyone else out of the water...",
